              <li><strong>Recommendation:</strong> Use a token for production projects</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h3>Creating a GitHub Token</h3>
          <ol>
            <li>Go to <a href="https://github.com/settings/tokens" target="_blank">GitHub Settings ‚Üí Developer settings ‚Üí Personal access tokens</a></li>
            <li>Generate a new token with <code>public_repo</code> permissions</li>
            <li>Use the token as the second parameter in <code>getRepoStats</code></li>
          </ol>
        </section>

